):

1. *Mogle* bi da odem kući ranije. (I could have gone home earlier.)
2. Ona je *mogla* da me čuje. (She could have heard me.)
3. *Mogli* smo da isplaniramo svoje putovanje u leto. (We could have planned our summer trip.)
4. *Mogle* su da me obaveste. (They could have informed me.)
5. *Moglo* je da se to izbegne. (It could have been avoided.)